* &quot;Chained Hands in Prayer&quot; (pf)
* &quot;For You I Sing This Song&quot; (cl in B flat, vn, vc, pf) (1976)
* &quot;Ji(t)&quot; (fl, pf)
* &quot;Sieben Rosen hat ein Strauch&quot; (vn)
